  "text": "(c) MHC analysis DNA was extracted from clipped spines using the DNeasy 96 Blood & Tissue Kit (Qiagen). MHC allele numbers were measured using Reference Strand-mediated Conformation Analysis (RSCA) as described [CITATION_1] .",
